	(text "LEDs + IR tap — badge_hw_design.md §LEDs and §Optical tap.\n4× SK9822 chained, capped at ~25% global brightness in firmware.\nOptical link: 940 nm LED direct-drive from GP9 (IR_TX) via R30=150Ω → ~12 mA pulsed at 38 kHz PIO carrier.\nRange is intentionally short (~2 cm) — face-to-face tap is the spec.\nTSOP4838 RX → active-low IR_RX. Place LED + RX mirror-symmetric on front face.\nOn contact, SK9822s pulse in unison with peer — that shared flash IS the sync confirmation." (exclude_from_sim no) (at 25.00 25.00 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top)) (uuid "6e1039b6-edf3-483c-9dc3-9ebdda6b4af8"))
